This is a randomized, open Label, balanced, two-treatment, two-period, two-sequence, single dose, cross over comparative pivotal study.

 The purpose of this study is to assess the bioequivalence between Test Product and the corresponding Reference Product under fasting condition in normal, healthy, adult, human male subjects.

